# Default-deny build context: ONLY the backend enters the image. This makes it
# structurally impossible for .env, node_modules, apps/web, tests, or local DB
# artifacts (tailor.db) to leak into a build -- new repo junk is excluded by
# default instead of needing a new ignore line.
*
.*
!app
!alembic
!alembic.ini
!main.py
!requirements.txt
!requirements.lock.txt
!scripts

# Junk inside the allowed trees.
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.DS_Store
